ree from [[Veer Bahadur Singh Purvanchal University]].<ref name=\"UPVS\"/>\n\n==Political career==\nDurga Prasad Yadav has been a [[Member of the Legislative Assembly (India)|MLA]] since 1985. he represented the [[Azamgarh (Assembly constituency)|Azamgarh]] constituency and is a member of the [[Samajwadi Party]].<ref>{{cite web | url=http://myneta.info/loksabha2004/candidate.php?candidate_id=3993 | title=Lok Sabha 2004 - Durga Prasad Yadav | publisher=myneta.info |accessdate=3 May 2019 }}</ref> He is one of the top leader of [[Samajwadi Party]].\n\n==Posts held==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! # !! From !! To !! Position !! Comments\n|-\n| 01 || 1985 || 1989 || Member, [[09th Legislative Assembly of Uttar Pradesh|09th Legislative Assembly]] ||\n|-\n| 02 || 1989 || 1991 || Member, [[10th Legislative Assembly of Uttar Pradesh|10th Legislative Assembly]] ||\n|-\n| 03 || 1991 || 1993 || Member, [[11th Legislative Assembly of Uttar Pradesh|11th Legislative Assembly]] ||\n|-\n| 04 || 1996 || 2002 || Member, [[13th Legislative Assembly of Uttar Pradesh|13th Legislative Assembly]] ||\n|-\n| 05 || 2002 || 2007 || Member, [[14th Legislative Assembly of Uttar Pradesh|14th Legislative Assembly]] ||\n|-\n| 06 || 2007 || 2012 || Member, [[15th Legislative Assembly of Uttar Pradesh|15th Legislative Assembly]] ||\n|-\n| 07 || 2012 || 2017 || Member, [[16th Legislative Assembly of Uttar Pradesh|16th Legislative Assembly]] ||\n|-\n| 08 || 2017 || Incumbent || Member, [[17th Legislative Assembly of Uttar Pradesh|17th Legislative Assembly]] ||\n|}\n\n==See also==\n*[[Azamgarh (Assembly constituency)|Azamgarh]]\n*[[Politics of India]]\n*[[Sixteenth Legislative Assembly of Uttar Pradesh]]\n*[[Uttar Pradesh Legislative Assembly]]\n{{Portal bar|India|Politics}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Yadav, Durga Prasad}}\n[[Category:1954 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Samajwadi Party politicians]]\n[[Category:Uttar Pradesh MLAs 2012\u20132017]]\n[[Cate